ie. Fresh examples tie together new material with the existing stories.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aGeneral Interest : General Interest. 4aHistory : Oral History. 4aLiterature : Folklore. 4aLiterature : Literary Theory. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / Essays.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143849038040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438490380423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438490380/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles